Package fileServer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IServe
    This interface is designed to allow HTTP requests interpreted by the Request Handler to be carried out.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CGI
    Execute php file and get the output.
    FileServer
    This file server implements IServer interface and handle Get, head Post request.
    FileStore
    Get the file as byte array on the local disk.
    HttpDateParser
    This is a help class for converting a HTTP-date string to Date.
    MediaType
    This is a help class to get Internet media type according to file name.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    HTTPFileNotFoundException
    This class provides a custom Exception that can be thrown if the file specified by the Request-URI does not exist.
    HTTPPermissionDeniedException
    This class provides a custom Exception that can be thrown if the file specified by the Request-URI exists but cannot be accessed.
    HTTPRuntimeException
    This class provides a custom Exception that can be thrown if the file specified by the Request-URI did not execute correctly.
